# PixelLab per-frame unit exports — packed into sprites.json + packed/ strips
# by `npm run pack:sprites`. The raw frames aren't imported by the runtime.
# `**` covers both base units (units/<faction>/<unit>/animations/) and
# promotion variants (units/<faction>/<unit>/paths/<path>/animations/), plus
# any other asset category that follows the same pack-from-frames pattern.
client/src/game-portal/src/assets/**/animations/
*.bak